<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coupon Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
        .bold{
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Special Offer Just For You!</h1>
    <p>Congratulations! You've received a special coupon for our App</p>
    <p>Coupon Code: <span class="bold">{{couponCode}}</span>  this coupon will grant you with {{percent}}% OFF!</p>
    <p>Hurry up this coupon will expire at <span class="bold">{{expirationDate}}</span> OR after the first <span class="bold">{{maxAmount}}</span> uses.</p>
    <p>Enjoy your shopping!</p>
</body>
</html>